Author Post


24 Feb 2020 14:22






This article was inspired by an unrelated conversation from my weekly tabletop game about making mountains out of molehills. Several pieces of this article are deliberately vague so as to make the researcher question the nature and severity of the SCP.

This article is also an homage to one late-May afternoon I spent in detention in grade school and a single goddamn fly the detention supervisor would not let me address.

I'd like to thank MalyceGraves for their crit assistance.







